00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:27,980
[Episode 26]

16
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:28,380
["To establish a heart for heaven and earth,]

17
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:28,750
[To guide the people's purpose in life,]

18
00:01:28,770 --> 00:01:29,330
[To carry forward the wisdom of ancient sages,]

19
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:29,690
[To pave the way for peace across generations."]

20
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:29,980
[by Zhang Zai, Northern Song Dynasty]

21
00:01:31,190 --> 00:01:32,270
Present the criminal,

22
00:01:32,270 --> 00:01:32,910
Zou Mian!

23
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:53,310
This man

24
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,160
is none other than the Southern Manufacturing Bureau's

25
00:01:55,230 --> 00:01:56,120
Zou Mian!

26
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,080
What's going on?

27
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,910
Can they hear us?

28
00:02:03,830 --> 00:02:04,590
No.

29
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:06,160
But since they haven't come down for so long,

30
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:07,830
they might be getting suspicious.

31
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,160
Let's go ashore first.

32
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,080
The raft is moving.

33
00:02:15,390 --> 00:02:16,190
Are they running away?

34
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,670
I knew it. It was a trap.

35
00:02:19,390 --> 00:02:21,670
I'll send someone to take them down.

36
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,320
Guards!

37
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,440
Take them down!

38
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:28,390
I'm so itchy.

39
00:02:31,670 --> 00:02:32,320
Sit tight.

40
00:02:32,830 --> 00:02:33,960
I'm so itchy.

41
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,030
Stop scratching!

42
00:02:37,830 --> 00:02:38,750
That's right.

43
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,800
That's the gesture.

44
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:46,470
Your Majesty, please forgive me!

45
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:53,960
Itchy...

46
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:54,880
Stop talking.

47
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:00,750
Zou Mian, you scoundrel,

48
00:03:01,390 --> 00:03:02,910
His Majesty just said

49
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,600
since you acted like this,

50
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,910
We don't need to meet again in this life!

51
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,270
Never see each other again!

52
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:12,030
Your Majesty, please forgive me!

53
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:13,520
Release the boat!

54
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,830
Right now, release the boat!

55
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,320
Release the boat!

56
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,270
Release the boat!

57
00:03:17,270 --> 00:03:19,270
Your Majesty, please forgive me!

58
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,160
This criminal

59
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:23,550
requests an audience with Your Majesty!

60
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,750
Father,

61
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,600
it's done.

62
00:03:28,110 --> 00:03:28,750
Nonsense!

63
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:33,240
Mr. Zou, how did you end up like this?

64
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,880
I'm wronged!

65
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,240
My lord,

66
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,360
don't listen to these untrustworthy people's

67
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,630
one-sided story.

68
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,360
I was escorting

69
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:44,190
the rare stone to the palace

70
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,630
when I was suddenly hijacked.

71
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:46,880
Not only did I end up here,

72
00:03:47,270 --> 00:03:50,960
but I was also falsely accused of corruption!

73
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:54,030
My lord,

74
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,320
please be discerning!

75
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:57,000
Sir, please calm down.

76
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:58,670
Dear,

77
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,550
you've overplayed this drama!

78
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,630
Zhao Buyou,

79
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:04,630
do you have any evidence

80
00:04:04,630 --> 00:04:05,550
for what you just said?

81
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,000
If not,

82
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:09,600
I won't allow you to act like this!

83
00:04:10,030 --> 00:04:11,320
Reporting to you, my lord,

84
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:14,240
I have a witness.

85
00:04:16,270 --> 00:04:17,070
Fine.

86
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,160
Bring him to Kaifeng Court for trial another day.

87
00:04:19,350 --> 00:04:20,830
Why can't we try him here?

88
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:22,040
Let's just try him here!

89
00:04:22,110 --> 00:04:23,000
Exactly!

90
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,110
Let's just try him here!

91
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,350
Bring the witness up!

92
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,270
Bring up the witness!

93
00:04:43,110 --> 00:04:44,320
Boss!

94
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:45,230
Boss!

95
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,480
The Imperial Guard Department...

96
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,200
The Imperial Guard Department is here to take Zou away!

97
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,640
Zou Mian!

98
00:04:58,110 --> 00:04:59,920
I also want to cut him into pieces,

99
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:03,040
but we should bring him to justice

100
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,880
and make his crimes known to all,

101
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:07,000
so the people of the East Capital will know his true face!

102
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:08,920
Make it known to all

103
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,200
and bring him to justice.

104
00:05:11,550 --> 00:05:12,160
Yes.

105
00:05:12,270 --> 00:05:13,350
Me too,

106
00:05:14,350 --> 00:05:15,920
but I can't do that.

107
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:28,510
Offer Mr. Zou a seat!

108
00:05:35,550 --> 00:05:36,230
What should we do?

109
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,200
It seems that the Imperial Guard Department has been bribed.

110
00:05:38,790 --> 00:05:40,200
As long as I'm still alive,

111
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:43,040
no one can interrupt

112
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,670
my buddy's trial today.

113
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,480
Kaifeng Court in session!

114
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:52,790
No admittance

115
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:54,320
to unauthorized personnel!

116
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,880
We're ordered by our superior

117
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,200
to take Mr. Zou back!

118
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,440
Get lost!

119
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:09,760
My lord,

120
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:12,160
may I question the witness?

121
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:14,600
Granted.

122
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:17,550
Witness,

123
00:06:17,790 --> 00:06:18,920
do you confess your guilt?

124
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,720
I...

125
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,440
I confess.

126
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:23,390
The Governor is right in front of you.

127
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:24,830
Tell him the truth

128
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:26,070
of what you know.

129
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:27,720
Try to get a lighter punishment.

130
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:31,950
My name

131
00:06:32,670 --> 00:06:33,760
is Zheng Dun.

132
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,200
For nearly a decade,

133
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,320
I've been instructed by the Zou family

134
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,550
to secretly find substitute scholars

135
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,440
for the Zou family's children

136
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:43,880
and kill them afterward

137
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,320
to silence them

138
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,950
and avoid future troubles.

139
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,510
But I didn't participate

140
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:52,390
in the killing.

141
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:54,790
Zou Mian was the one who instructed it.

142
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:56,600
Okay.

143
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:58,550
Zheng Dun,

144
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,950
is this Zou Mian you mentioned on the stage?

145
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:07,550
Master!

146
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,640
I didn't know you were here.

147
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,880
I really didn't know you were here.

148
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,160
Our Zou family

149
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,000
is a scholarly family that has produced many talents.

150
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:18,720
But now we're being slandered by this scoundrel.

151
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,320
My lord,

152
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:22,790
please be discerning!

153
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,070
Get out of the way!

154
00:07:29,110 --> 00:07:30,350
We're all on the same side, no need to draw weapons!

155
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:32,440
Master, please give me another chance!

156
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,350
I don't want to die...

157
00:07:33,350 --> 00:07:35,270
I really don't want to die...

158
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:35,720
I don't want to die...

159
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,320
Zheng Dun!

160
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:36,760
I don't want to die...

161
00:07:37,670 --> 00:07:38,230
Here.

162
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,950
Was what you just said true?

163
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,040
They... they forced me to do it!

164
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:44,670
They forced me to do it!

165
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,270
They forced me to do it!

166
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,640
Why is his testimony inconsistent?

167
00:07:49,110 --> 00:07:50,320
They forced me...

168
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,390
Yeah. Why is it inconsistent?

169
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,760
...to frame the Zou family.

170
00:07:52,830 --> 00:07:53,920
The Zou family has nothing

171
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,720
to do with this!

172
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:57,350
Nothing at all!

173
00:08:26,230 --> 00:08:26,950
Zhao Buyou,

174
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:28,670
the witness has retracted his confession,

175
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,000
which means the testimony needs further verification.

176
00:08:31,790 --> 00:08:33,320
If you don't have any new evidence,

177
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,000
I'll end this drama

178
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:37,230
here today.

179
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,110
Wait!

180
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:40,200
My lord,

181
00:08:41,670 --> 00:08:42,640
I still have physical evidence.

182
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:43,910
Present the physical evidence!

183
00:08:45,110 --> 00:08:46,440
Father, sit down.

184
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,320
Be patient.

185
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,280
What is this?

186
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,910
Zou Mian,

187
00:08:59,030 --> 00:09:01,080
do you recognize this gown?

188
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,440
How would I recognize it?

189
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:07,400
This is the gown that your daughter Zou Ziyin

190
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:10,150
was wearing the last time she met you.

191
00:09:10,590 --> 00:09:12,000
She probably didn't expect

192
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:14,110
that meeting with her father

193
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:16,080
would be her last.

194
00:09:16,150 --> 00:09:17,150
Zhao Buyou!

195
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,840
Don't slander me.

196
00:09:19,470 --> 00:09:20,400
Ziyin

197
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:24,520
clearly died of the disease in prison.

198
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,520
Is the autopsy report out?

199
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,440
Yes.

200
00:09:34,470 --> 00:09:35,280
My lord,

201
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,760
I'd like to request

202
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:38,910
that the coroner of Kaifeng Court

203
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:40,880
announce the cause of Zou Ziyin's death

204
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:41,840
to the public.

205
00:09:46,350 --> 00:09:46,910
Granted.

206
00:09:54,230 --> 00:09:56,960
I'm Coroner Yao He of Kaifeng Court.

207
00:09:57,590 --> 00:09:59,840
Zou Ziyin, daughter of Zou Mian

208
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:02,350
from the Southern Manufacturing Bureau, and her husband Luan Hui

209
00:10:02,350 --> 00:10:05,000
didn't die from the disease,

210
00:10:05,590 --> 00:10:07,200
but from poisoning.

211
00:10:07,710 --> 00:10:09,150
And the so-called disease

212
00:10:09,470 --> 00:10:12,150
was just a cover-up!

213
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,350
Zou Mian,

214
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,710
to protect yourself,

215
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,960
you even killed your own daughter!

216
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,760
Shut up.

217
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:22,760
Do you

218
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,470
recognize this?

219
00:10:25,790 --> 00:10:26,440
Everyone,

220
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,230
this is a coin.

221
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:30,760
[Longevity and Good Health]

222
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,280
Four characters are engraved on it:

223
00:10:32,710 --> 00:10:34,150
Longevity and Good Health.

224
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:36,550
When you gave it

225
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,440
to your daughter,

226
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:39,760
I believe

227
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,030
you were also a father who loved his daughter.

228
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,400
You never expected

229
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,320
that your daughter would die in front of you

230
00:10:49,350 --> 00:10:50,880
wearing this coin.

231
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,790
You have no conscience at all!

232
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:56,790
Return Ziyin's belongings

233
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,640
to me!

234
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,590
You don't deserve to be a father!

235
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:08,910
Ziyin...

236
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:12,580
[Longevity and Good Health]

237
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,440
You beast.

238
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,150
Even a tiger won't eat its cubs.

239
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:18,790
Are you even human?

240
00:11:19,710 --> 00:11:20,760
You're worse than a beast!

241
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:22,590
No matter how you repent,

242
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:24,200
your daughter won't hear it.

243
00:11:24,590 --> 00:11:25,230
Zou Mian,

244
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,880
you don't deserve to be a father!

245
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,080
Scum!

246
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:30,080
He's worse than a beast!

247
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,440
You won't escape self-blame

248
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:33,760
for the rest of your life.

249
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:44,910
Why should I blame myself?

250
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,590
Ziyin

251
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:51,550
did commit suicide at my persuasion.

252
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,840
I was upholding justice

253
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:55,470
for the people

254
00:11:55,470 --> 00:11:58,640
and eliminating a threat for His Majesty!

255
00:11:58,640 --> 00:11:59,790
He's still making excuses!

256
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,960
Over the years,

257
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:06,230
Ziyin was misled by her husband Luan Hui

258
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:09,670
to do many harmful things,

259
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:14,710
making me unable to face His Majesty and the people.

260
00:12:14,710 --> 00:12:17,280
Their refusal to confess wasn't enough to ease public anger.

261
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:20,590
Between family and justice,

262
00:12:20,590 --> 00:12:22,320
I chose justice!

263
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:23,960
Zhao Buyou,

264
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:27,350
you targeted me everywhere!

265
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:29,470
You're just a mere litigator,

266
00:12:30,790 --> 00:12:32,910
yet you dare to be so arrogant.

267
00:12:32,910 --> 00:12:33,790
Who is

268
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:35,710
behind you?

269
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,640
Zhao Buyou,

270
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:38,350
what are your intentions?

271
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:40,880
You even dared to stop the Imperial Guard Department!

272
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:43,840
Are you tired of living?

273
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:45,280
I'll kill you.

274
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:46,910
Get up!

275
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:12,310
There's some chaos over there by the stage.

276
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:13,940
Could Buyou and the others be there?

277
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:25,260
You two wait for me here.

278
00:13:25,430 --> 00:13:26,350
Don't run around.

279
00:13:26,470 --> 00:13:27,260
Wen Yue...

280
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:28,870
Just now,

281
00:13:29,430 --> 00:13:32,380
Mr. Li mentioned the Shipbuilder Su Zhi from the Taihu Shipyard.

282
00:13:33,350 --> 00:13:34,620
When he was killed,

283
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:37,910
he had a daughter

284
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,550
named Wen Yue.

285
00:13:43,470 --> 00:13:44,940
She's my wife.

286
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:49,910
Chief Minister of Office of Justice, Dong Qian,

287
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:52,470
left behind a son and a daughter after his death.

288
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:55,580
They're the younger brother and sister I adopted.

289
00:13:55,740 --> 00:13:57,140
The honest official Li Yan

290
